                image of <m>A</m>, the label <m>J</m> to the image of <m>B</m>, etc.
                You may be able to rename these images to <m>A'</m>, <m>B'</m>, etc.,
                or you may want to note that in the discussion that follows, <m>A'=I</m>,
                <m>B'=J</m>, <m>C'=K</m>, <m>D'=L</m>, <m>E'=M</m>, and <m>F'=N</m>.
            </p>
        </aside>
        <!--FIX THIS AFTER I TRY TO REVISE THE GEOGEBRA APP!!!!!!!!!!-->
        <p>
            In what ways are the reflected image <m>A'B'C'D'E'F'</m> and the original 
